snippet.title: KonoSuba: Fantastic Days | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Sign up for updates on https://playkonosuba.com/
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/playkonosuba
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playkonosuba/
An epic journey that transports you to another world in the perfect blend of comedy, fantasy, and action. This highly anticipated mobile RPG will soon be available globally in 2021!
